description: This file defines a Qwik component named `RouterHead` that manages the document's `<head>` content, utilizing hooks to access document head data and location information, and rendering dynamic head elements such as title, meta tags, links, styles, and scripts.

methods.name: RouterHead
methods.description: A Qwik component that renders the contents of the document's `<head>` based on current document head data and location.
